meta_description: "The Ameswell Hotel offers uncommon luxury in Silicon Valley. Nestled on 11 acres in sunny Mountain View, we bring together technology and innovation, natural beauty and an opportunity to play unlike any other hotel in the Bay Area."
canonical_href: https://www.theameswellhotel.com
